Car Central 🚗💨
A modern car dealership website built with React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, and AOS (Animate on Scroll). This project showcases various car models, their specifications, and a seamless user experience with smooth animations.

✨ Features
🔥 Fast & Optimized – Built with Vite for lightning-fast performance

🎨 Responsive UI – Styled with Tailwind CSS for a modern look

⚡ Smooth Animations – Integrated AOS for engaging scroll animations

🏎️ Car Listings – Display detailed car models and specifications

📱 Mobile-Friendly – Fully responsive for all screen sizes

🔍 Search & Filter – Easily find the perfect car

📩 Contact Form – Get in touch with the dealership

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: React.js + Vite

Styling: Tailwind CSS

Animations: AOS (Animate on Scroll)

